snippet.textDisplay: Hey rick see if you can find a club called a maxfli black missile.  I used to have one back in highschool, and it always seemed like the biggest cheater club ever.  I bought it as a joke, cause it looked like an old wooden club, but it had a carbon graphite fiber head or something weird like that, so it wasnt actually wood.  Anyway, i was a decent golfer back then, but hardly a pro.  and that maxfli black missile i bought was a 3-wood, that i could hit 310 yards straight down the fairway every time i hit it.  it was the most ridiculous club ever until the day that it broke.  but with all my research over the years, i have never been able to find this club again.
